=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_LFPulse_ex5 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 200 Hz, featuring punchy attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 200.0000
  harmonic_decay_rate: -7.7453
  harmonic_regularity: 0.5366
  pitch_clarity: 18.1457
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -10.5953
  resonance_freq: 1248.9258

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: LFPulse Example 5
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Classes/LFPulse.html
// Tags: LFPulse, Classes, oscillator, modulation
// ---
// --- Example 5 ---
{ LFPulse.ar(LFPulse.kr(3, 0, 0.3, 200, 200), 0, 0.2, 0.1) }.play;
